","msg":"國籍：chinese<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gov.hk/sc/residents/immigration/images/personal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Fsc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Fimages%2Fpersonal.jpg&h=f2365ffc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc7dabdda1b8dc4a7652d7d9ff4f86a4ef4786c6","tid":791841,"uid":59014,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b083f3dd72ccb5dc82f90ddfbb6d35d1b7ad6a86","tid":791841,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5e934d51c3ccd70cc07b1374433bab8c0e16fd05","tid":791841,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d376491d51c6eaa3aa44dc8580eb6f665f4d15f5","tid":791841,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"來香港過冷河<br />\n攞番個香港身份證及護照咪得囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"香港護照上寫嘅國籍係咩先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等睇遲啲連香港人都唔入得去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"國籍：chinese<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gov.hk/sc/residents/immigration/images/personal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Fsc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Fimages%2Fpersonal.jpg&h=f2365ffc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好講事實出黎啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過係連登講無用 全部BNO BC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34b109ecce831b8c5e53cf965f5057c01b41ead","tid":791841,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"圍剿支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d3770909cbd3eac93fcfcf7f9d4032ad477ddd","tid":791841,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"中國人的榮耀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16223b72d2cac3b4130fc682fc8208c8155d5a11","tid":791841,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:33:24.000Z","msg":"e form係香港,中國分開<br />\n<br />\n但問題係年年赤化,殖民你賤格香港人唔理<br />\n<br />\n個撚個特區護照比人踢爆同大陸官方接觸<br />\n<br />\n好快玩完"},{"pid":"e6bd089095295f1833f8e454fa855f99b15b8ac1","tid":791841,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"針對這件事，半導體行業觀察向ASML官方求證。他們嚴正表示：<br />\n<br />\n這是個不實傳言，<br />\n<br />\nThis is not true，<br />\n<br />\nASML招人的時候一般不會有國籍限制，<br />\n<br />\nASML would like to emphasize that there is no general restriction in hiring any nationality.<br />\n<br />\n我們歡迎來自全球各地的工程師。<br />\n<br />\nWe welcome engineers from all over the world。<br />\n<br />\nASML可以並將持續歡迎符合職位需求的中國籍人員加入公司高科技產品的研發、工藝和服務團隊。<br />\n<br />\nASML can hire and is still hiring Chinese nationals who can work on  ASML&rsquo;s high tech products in development, engineering, service etc - also in the Netherlands.<br />\n<br />\n但是他們也表示，對於ASML某些在美國本土開發的高新技術，包括中國在內的大約二十個國家的人需要先獲得美國的相關許可證，ASML才能將其招進這些技術的相關團隊。<br />\n<br />\nHowever, for certain technologies (that were originally developed in the US) Chinese nationals (as well as nationals from roughly 20 other countries) require a US export license before ASML can assign these employees to work on these technologies.<br />\n<br />\n但這並非新出的規定，事實上美國在多年前就已開始實施。<br />\n<br />\nThis is not a new situation as this has been the procedure for years.<br />\n<br />\nASML進一步指出，當然這個規定目前看來有較過去嚴格的趨勢。<br />\n<br />\nUnder the current US administration, the conditions for granting the permits have become stricter and the procedure takes more time.<br />\n<br />\n好似澄清左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0104896d40160119339e325daeb850937770df","tid":791841,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:36:02.000Z","msg":"人類總是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a64e2f6648d71c86d4588511003f1996d3682c4","tid":791841,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:37:03.000Z","msg":"就算公司批 美國一定唔批啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dced5bc9320834956da4fc059b93d305f83967","tid":791841,"uid":5574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc7dabdda1b8dc4a7652d7d9ff4f86a4ef4786c6","tid":791841,"uid":59014,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b083f3dd72ccb5dc82f90ddfbb6d35d1b7ad6a86","tid":791841,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5e934d51c3ccd70cc07b1374433bab8c0e16fd05","tid":791841,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"香港護照上寫嘅國籍係咩先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等睇遲啲連香港人都唔入得去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"國籍：chinese<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gov.hk/sc/residents/immigration/images/personal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Fsc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Fimages%2Fpersonal.jpg&h=f2365ffc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\